model

Class Board

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Board
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoardDynamic, BoardStatic

    public abstract class Board
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class which contains the method to create a board. The board class allows you to change the state of the cell, and count its neighbors.
    Author:
    Ali Arfan, Kent Erlend Bratteng Knudsen, Stian Tornholm Grimsgaard
    See Also:
    GameBoard
